==== test correct usage ====
class <emptyTree><<C <root>>> < (::<todo sym>)
  ::T::Sig::WithoutRuntime.sig() do ||
    <self>.params(:x, <emptyTree>::<C Object>).returns(<emptyTree>::<C Integer>)
  end

  def demo<<todo method>>(x, &<blk>)
    ::<root>::<C T>.cast(x, <emptyTree>::<C String>)
  end
end
==== test error with unset parser ====
RBS mode is only supported when parsing with Prism. Please add `--parser=prism` to your Sorbet config.
==== test error with original parser ====
RBS mode is only supported when parsing with Prism. Please add `--parser=prism` to your Sorbet config.
